sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant Notif as Notification Service
    participant Redis
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over Client, Notif: Step 1: Request OTP
    Client->>Notif: POST /notifications/password-reset/otp (Email)
    Notif->>Redis: Store OTP (5 min)
    Notif-->>Client: OTP Sent via Email

    Note over Client, DB: Step 2: Reset Password with OTP
    Client->>Auth: POST /auth/reset-password (Email, NewPass, OTP)
    Auth->>Notif: POST /notifications/password-reset/validate (Email, OTP)
    Notif->>Redis: Check & Delete OTP
    Redis-->>Notif: Valid/Invalid
    Notif-->>Auth: Boolean Result
    
    alt is OTP Valid
        Auth->>DB: Update User Password
        Auth-->>Client: 200 OK (Success)
    else is OTP Invalid
        Auth-->>Client: 400 Bad Request (Invalid OTP)
    end
